  "detailed_description": "An RPG, a platformer, a survival horror, a strategy game, a life simulation and a space shooter... Just what exactly is this game? One thing's for sure: it's a love story that bends and transcends genres.<br><br>Play as Isiah to survive a haunted prison, leap through a mystic forest, wage war against a kingdom, furnish the happiest home and fly through space: all for a chance to see Tia again.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A special story<br></li><li> Multiple worlds with their own rules, games within a game<br></li><li> Homages to popular video games<br></li><li> A unique take on the turn-based battle system<br></li><li> Master classes, summons & the custom stat system</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996230/extras/3cfbf5e523babb68074c676c72364527.poster.avif?t=1713440639\" width=426 height=319 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/996230/extras/3cfbf5e523babb68074c676c72364527.webm?t=1713440639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
